# Hugo build output — Actions builds this, don't commit it
public/
resources/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Hugo temp files
.hugo_build.lock
```

Create this as `.gitignore` in the root of your project. Your repo will then only contain:
```
.github/workflows/deploy.yml   ← tells Actions how to build
hugo.toml                      ← your config
themes/hugo-theme-stack/       ← the theme (as a submodule reference)
content/                       ← your posts and pages
static/                        ← images, avatar, etc.